title: [Feywrot Mire, Banyan Cirque]
description: Domed canvas tents, brightly striped in yellows, reds, and blues have displaced much of the natural vegetation here.  Wire cages of chickens and turkeys resting between the tents seem to be responsible for both the noise and the odors permeating the area.  A pig wrangler stands with arms crossed watching some greased pigs corralled behind a chain-link fence.

Domed canvas tents, brightly striped in yellows, reds, and blues have displaced much of the natural vegetation here.  Wire cages of chickens and turkeys resting between the tents seem to be responsible for both the noise and the odors permeating the area.
